DARKROCK
I imagine it’s not difficult for you to open the upper section of the fridge, what do you think?

SAYLOR
Oh don’t bother trying to do it.  This fridge sucks.

SAYLOR (CONT’D)
I’ve never heard any other fridge to make such a pithy noise.  Pithy and pitiful.  “Please dispose of me mercilessly!  Just like that poor time machine next to me.  Throw a giant fireball at me to make me feel alive again for the remaining few seconds!"  I have no idea why I’m lugging around this pile of metal at all, nowhere in all of vast time and space could I find a scrapyard.  Throwing this thing into a time vortex is kind of pathetic, I’m against space debris with all my heart.  As humankind, we should--

DARKROCK
--Please stop.

SAYLOR (CONT'D)
...be kind.

DARKROCK
Fridge, Saylor.

SAYLOR
Door, Darkrock.

